psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.impl.minimal

Class MinimalBioactiveEntityEnricher

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FullBioactiveEntityEnricher

    public class MinimalBioactiveEntityEnricher
extends AbstractInteractorEnricher<BioactiveEntity>
    A basic minimal enricher for bioactive entities. See description of minimal enrichment in AbstractInteractorEnricher. The bioactive entities fetcher is required for enriching bioactive entities.
    Since:
    07/08/13
    Author:
    Gabriel Aldam (galdam@ebi.ac.uk)

      • MinimalBioactiveEntityEnricher

        public MinimalBioactiveEntityEnricher(BioactiveEntityFetcher fetcher)

        Parameters:
        fetcher - The fetcher used to collect bioactiveEntity records.
